  "remarks": "\nAnatoly Ilyich BIBILOV i\ns an involved person under the Russia (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019 on the following ground: Anatoly Ilyich BIBILOV is or has been involved in \ndestabilising Ukraine or undermining or threatening the territorial integrity, sovereignty or independence of Ukraine because he engages in, provides support for, or promotes any policy or action which destabilises Ukraine or undermines or threatens the territorial integrity, sovereignty or independence of Ukraine.\n",
